arn.description: Amazon Resource Name used for identifying the default route table in API operations

id.description: Unique identifier for referencing the default route table in other configurations

owner_id.description: AWS account ID of the resource owner, useful for access control and auditing

route.description: Details of the routes defined in the default route table for traffic management

tags_all.description: Comprehensive list of tags attached to the default route table for resource organization

vpc_id.description: Identifier of the VPC linked to the default route table for network association
